parameters.name: filters
parameters.description: Information about filters to apply to narrow the results returned in the list. (dict) --- nformation about the filter used to narrow the results returned in a list of projects. A key that can be used to sort results. The values of the key. (string) --- comparisonOperator (string) --- The operator used to compare the fields.

nested_params.name: key
nested_params.description: A key that can be used to sort results.

nested_params.name: comparisonOperator
nested_params.description: The operator used to compare the fields.

nested_items.name: nextToken
nested_items.description: A token returned from a call to this API to indicate the next batch of results to return, if any.

nested_items.name: name
nested_items.description: The name of the project in the space.

nested_items.name: displayName
nested_items.description: The friendly name displayed to users of the project in Amazon CodeCatalyst.
